TSCC_55.Description: Sum of scores of items 2, 15, 24, 25, 32, 33, 39, 41, and 50. Generalized anxiety, hyperarousal, worry, specific fears (e.g. of men, women, or both; of the dark, of being killed); episodes of free-floating anxiety; and a sense of impending danger. | Calculation = [TSCC_02] + [TSCC_15] + [TSCC_24] + [TSCC_25] + [TSCC_32] + [TSCC_33] + [TSCC_39] + [TSCC_41] + [TSCC_50]

TSCC_56.Description: Sum of scores of items 7, 9, 14, 20, 26, 27, 28, 42, and 52. Feelings of sadness, unhappiness, and loneliness; episodes of tearfulness; depressive cognitions such as guilt and self-denigration; and self-injuriousness and suicidality. | Calculation = [TSCC_07] + [TSCC_9] + [TSCC_14] + [TSCC_20] + [TSCC_26] + [TSCC_27] + [TSCC_28] + [TSCC_42] + [TSCC_52]

TSCC_57.Description: Sum of scores of items 6, 13, 16, 19, 21, 36, 37, 46, and 49. Angry thoughts, feelings, and behaviors, including feeling mad, feeling mean and hating others; having difficulty de-escalating anger; wanting to yell at or hurt people; arguing or fighting. | Calculation = [TSCC_06] + [TSCC_13] + [TSCC_16] + [TSCC_19] + [TSCC_21] + [TSCC_36] + [TSCC_37] + [TSCC_46] + [TSCC_49]

TSCC_58.Description: Sum of scores of items 1, 3, 10, 11, 12, 24, 25, 35, 43 and 51. Posttraumatic symptoms including intrusive thoughts, sensations, and memories of painful past events; nightmares; fears; and cognitive avoidance of painful. | Calculation = [TSCC_01] + [TSCC_03] + [TSCC_10] + [TSCC_11] + [TSCC_12] + [TSCC_24] + [TSCC_25] + [TSCC_35] + [TSCC_43] + [TSCC_51]

TSCC_59.Description: Sum of scores of items 5, 11, 18, 29, 30, 31, 38, 45, 48, and 53. Dissociative symptomatology, including derealization; one’s mind going blank; emotional numbing; pretending to be someone else or somewhere else; day-dreaming; memory problems and dissociative avoidance. | Calculation = [TSCC_05] + [TSCC_11] + [TSCC_18] + [TSCC_29] + [TSCC_30] + [TSCC_31] + [TSCC_38] + [TSCC_45] + [TSCC_48] + [TSCC_53]

TSCC_60.Description: Subscale of dissociation. Sum of scores of items 11, 18, 29, 30, 31, 45, and 48. | Calculation = [TSCC_11] + [TSCC_18] + [TSCC_29] + [TSCC_30] + [TSCC_31] + [TSCC_45] + [TSCC_48]

TSCC_61.Description: Score Subscale of dissociation. Sum of scores of items 5, 38, and 53. | Calculation = [TSCC_05] + [TSCC_38] + [TSCC_53]

TSCC_62.Description: Sum of scores of items 4, 8, 17, 22, 23, 34, 40, 44, 47, and 54. Sexual thoughts or feelings that are atypical when they occur earlier than expected or with greater than normal frequency; sexual conflicts; negative responses to sexual stimuli; and fear of being sexually exploited. | Calculation = [TSCC_04] + [TSCC_08] + [TSCC_17] + [TSCC_22] + [TSCC_23] + [TSCC_34] + [TSCC_40] + [TSCC_44] + [TSCC_47] + [TSCC_54]

TSCC_63.Description: Subscale of sexual concerns. Sum of scores of items 4, 8, 17, 22, 23, 44, and 47. | Calculation = [TSCC_04] + [TSCC_08] + [TSCC_17] + [TSCC_22] + [TSCC_23] + [TSCC_44] + [TSCC_47]

TSCC_64.Description: Subscale of sexual concerns. Sum of scores of items 23, 34, 40, and 54. | Calculation = [TSCC_23] + [TSCC_34] + [TSCC_40] + [TSCC_54]

TSCC_65.Description:
If any of the questions 1, 2, 6, 9, 10, 19, 28, 41, 49, and 53 are marked 0 or unanswered, then the item earns the score of 1, and the scores are summed. A high score reflects a tendency toward denial, a general under endorsement response set, or a need to appear unusually symptom-free. | Calculation = iif([TSCC_01]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_02]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_06]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_9]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_10]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_19]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_28]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_41]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_49]==0,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_53]==0,'1','0')

TSCC_66.Description:
If any of the questions 1, 18, 24, 25, 26, 27, 39, and 45 are marked 0 or unanswered, then the item earns the score of 1, and the scores are summed. A high score indicates a general over response to TSCC items, a specific need to appear especially symptomatic, or a state of being overwhelmed by traumatic stress. | Calculation = iif([TSCC_01]==3,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_18]==3,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_24]==3,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_25]==3,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_26]==3,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_27]==3,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_39]==3,'1','0')+
iif([TSCC_45]==3,'1','0')
